    }
   },
   "source": [
    "## Notebooks\n",
    "* python is the name of the interpreter\n",
    "* ipython is an interactive interpreter\n",
    "* A notebook like this one is a grapical interactive environment. \n",
    "* Use print(.) to output variables on the screen. \n",
    "* To navigate the filesystem (% indicates a notebook command)\n",
    "```python\n",
    "%ls\n",
    "%mkdir test\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": "slide"
    }
   },
   "source": [
